---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Section from '../components/Section.astro';
---

<Layout title="Transparência" description="Transparência financeira da A.R.L.S Enoch - Extratos e destinação das doações">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="gradient-animated text-white py-20 relative overflow-hidden particles-bg">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-blue-subtle opacity-90"></div>
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 animate-fade-in-up bg-gradient-to-r from-white via-blue-100 to-white bg-clip-text text-transparent drop-shadow-lg text-gradient-animated">
        Transparência
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-blue-100 animate-fade-in-up drop-shadow-md" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
        Acompanhe como utilizamos os recursos recebidos através das doações
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Resumo Financeiro -->
  <Section
    title="Resumo Financeiro"
    subtitle="Visão geral dos recursos recebidos e destinados"
    className="bg-white"
  >
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-8">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50 to-green-100 p-6 rounded-lg border-2 border-green-200 shadow-md">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500 to-green-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-medium bg-gradient-to-r from-green-600 to-green-700 bg-clip-text text-transparent font-semibold mb-2">
            Total Recebido
          </h3>
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-green-600 via-green-700 to-green-800 bg-clip-text text-transparent drop-shadow-sm text-gradient-glow">
            R$ 0,00
          </p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-2 font-medium">Período: <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-600 to-gray-700 bg-clip-text text-transparent font-semibold">2024</span></p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-blue-100 p-6 rounded-lg border-2 border-blue-200 shadow-md">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-medium bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-blue-700 bg-clip-text text-transparent font-semibold mb-2">
            Total Destinado
          </h3>
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 via-blue-700 to-blue-800 bg-clip-text text-transparent drop-shadow-sm text-gradient-glow">
            R$ 0,00
          </p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-2 font-medium">100% <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-blue-700 bg-clip-text text-transparent font-semibold">dos recursos</span></p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-purple-100 p-6 rounded-lg border-2 border-purple-200 shadow-md">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-purple-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-medium bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-purple-700 bg-clip-text text-transparent font-semibold mb-2">
            Beneficiados
          </h3>
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 via-purple-700 to-purple-800 bg-clip-text text-transparent drop-shadow-sm text-gradient-glow">
            0
          </p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-2 font-medium"><span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-purple-700 bg-clip-text text-transparent font-semibold">Famílias atendidas</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <!-- Extratos Mensais -->
  <Section
    title="Extratos Mensais"
    subtitle="Detalhamento mensal das receitas e despesas"
    className="bg-gray-50"
  >
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="overflow-x-auto">
          <table class="w-full">
            <thead class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 via-blue-700 to-blue-800 text-white">
              <tr>
                <th class="px-6 py-4 text-left text-sm font-semibold bg-gradient-to-r from-white/90 to-white bg-clip-text text-transparent drop-shadow-sm">
                  Mês/Ano
                </th>
                <th class="px-6 py-4 text-right text-sm font-semibold bg-gradient-to-r from-white/90 to-white bg-clip-text text-transparent drop-shadow-sm">
                  Receitas
                </th>
                <th class="px-6 py-4 text-right text-sm font-semibold bg-gradient-to-r from-white/90 to-white bg-clip-text text-transparent drop-shadow-sm">
                  Despesas
                </th>
                <th class="px-6 py-4 text-right text-sm font-semibold bg-gradient-to-r from-white/90 to-white bg-clip-text text-transparent drop-shadow-sm">
                  Saldo
                </th>
                <th class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-sm font-semibold bg-gradient-to-r from-white/90 to-white bg-clip-text text-transparent drop-shadow-sm">
                  Ações
                </th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-200">
              <tr class="hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-sm font-medium bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-800 to-gray-900 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
                  Janeiro/2024
                </td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-sm text-right bg-gradient-to-r from-green-600 to-green-700 bg-clip-text text-transparent font-semibold">
                  R$ 0,00
                </td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-sm text-right bg-gradient-to-r from-red-600 to-red-700 bg-clip-text text-transparent font-semibold">
                  R$ 0,00
                </td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-sm text-right font-semibold bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 via-blue-700 to-blue-800 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
                  R$ 0,00
                </td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center">
                  <button class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-blue-700 bg-clip-text text-transparent hover:from-blue-700 hover:to-blue-800 text-sm font-semibold transition-all duration-300" onclick="alert('Extrato em breve')">
                    Ver Detalhes
                  </button>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors bg-gray-50/50">
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-sm font-medium bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-800 to-gray-900 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
                  Fevereiro/2024
                </td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-sm text-right bg-gradient-to-r from-green-600 to-green-700 bg-clip-text text-transparent font-semibold">
                  R$ 0,00
                </td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-sm text-right bg-gradient-to-r from-red-600 to-red-700 bg-clip-text text-transparent font-semibold">
                  R$ 0,00
                </td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-sm text-right font-semibold bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 via-blue-700 to-blue-800 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
                  R$ 0,00
                </td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center">
                  <button class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-blue-700 bg-clip-text text-transparent hover:from-blue-700 hover:to-blue-800 text-sm font-semibold transition-all duration-300" onclick="alert('Extrato em breve')">
                    Ver Detalhes
                  </button>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-sm font-medium bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-800 to-gray-900 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
                  Março/2024
                </td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-sm text-right bg-gradient-to-r from-green-600 to-green-700 bg-clip-text text-transparent font-semibold">
                  R$ 0,00
                </td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-sm text-right bg-gradient-to-r from-red-600 to-red-700 bg-clip-text text-transparent font-semibold">
                  R$ 0,00
                </td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-sm text-right font-semibold bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 via-blue-700 to-blue-800 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
                  R$ 0,00
                </td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center">
                  <button class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-blue-700 bg-clip-text text-transparent hover:from-blue-700 hover:to-blue-800 text-sm font-semibold transition-all duration-300" onclick="alert('Extrato em breve')">
                    Ver Detalhes
                  </button>
                </td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 px-6 py-4 border-t border-gray-200">
          <p class="text-sm text-center">
            <em class="bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-600 via-gray-700 to-gray-800 bg-clip-text text-transparent font-medium">
              Os extratos são atualizados mensalmente. Para mais informações, entre em contato conosco.
            </em>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <!-- Destinação das Doações -->
  <Section
    title="Destinação das Doações"
    subtitle="Como os recursos são aplicados em nossos projetos e ações"
    className="bg-white"
  >
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border-2 border-gray-200 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-500 to-orange-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-600 via-orange-700 to-orange-800 bg-clip-text text-transparent mb-1 drop-shadow-sm text-gradient-glow">
                Assistência Social
              </h3>
              <p class="text-sm bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-600 to-gray-700 bg-clip-text text-transparent font-medium">
                Auxílio a famílias em situação de vulnerabilidade
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-4">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-2">
              <span class="text-sm bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-600 to-gray-700 bg-clip-text text-transparent font-medium">
                Percentual destinado
              </span>
              <span class="text-sm font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-600 to-orange-700 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
                0%
              </span>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full bg-gray-200 rounded-full h-2">
              <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500 via-orange-600 to-orange-700 h-2 rounded-full shadow-sm" style="width: 0%"></div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-2 font-medium">
              Valor: <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-600 to-orange-700 bg-clip-text text-transparent font-semibold">R$ 0,00</span>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border-2 border-gray-200 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500 to-green-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-green-600 via-green-700 to-green-800 bg-clip-text text-transparent mb-1 drop-shadow-sm text-gradient-glow">
                Projetos Educacionais
              </h3>
              <p class="text-sm bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-600 to-gray-700 bg-clip-text text-transparent font-medium">
                Programas de educação e capacitação
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-4">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-2">
              <span class="text-sm bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-600 to-gray-700 bg-clip-text text-transparent font-medium">
                Percentual destinado
              </span>
              <span class="text-sm font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-green-600 to-green-700 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
                0%
              </span>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full bg-gray-200 rounded-full h-2">
              <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500 via-green-600 to-green-700 h-2 rounded-full shadow-sm" style="width: 0%"></div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-2 font-medium">
              Valor: <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-600 to-green-700 bg-clip-text text-transparent font-semibold">R$ 0,00</span>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border-2 border-gray-200 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-red-500 to-red-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-red-600 via-red-700 to-red-800 bg-clip-text text-transparent mb-1 drop-shadow-sm text-gradient-glow">
                Ações de Saúde
              </h3>
              <p class="text-sm bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-600 to-gray-700 bg-clip-text text-transparent font-medium">
                Campanhas e atendimentos de saúde
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-4">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-2">
              <span class="text-sm bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-600 to-gray-700 bg-clip-text text-transparent font-medium">
                Percentual destinado
              </span>
              <span class="text-sm font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-red-600 to-red-700 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
                0%
              </span>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full bg-gray-200 rounded-full h-2">
              <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-red-500 via-red-600 to-red-700 h-2 rounded-full shadow-sm" style="width: 0%"></div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-2 font-medium">
              Valor: <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-red-600 to-red-700 bg-clip-text text-transparent font-semibold">R$ 0,00</span>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border-2 border-gray-200 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-purple-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M20 7l-8-4-8 4m16 0l-8 4m8-4v10l-8 4m0-10L4 7m8 4v10M4 7v10l8 4" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 via-purple-700 to-purple-800 bg-clip-text text-transparent mb-1 drop-shadow-sm text-gradient-glow">
                Infraestrutura
              </h3>
              <p class="text-sm bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-600 to-gray-700 bg-clip-text text-transparent font-medium">
                Manutenção e melhorias das instalações
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-4">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-2">
              <span class="text-sm bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-600 to-gray-700 bg-clip-text text-transparent font-medium">
                Percentual destinado
              </span>
              <span class="text-sm font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-purple-700 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
                0%
              </span>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full bg-gray-200 rounded-full h-2">
              <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 via-purple-600 to-purple-700 h-2 rounded-full shadow-sm" style="width: 0%"></div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-2 font-medium">
              Valor: <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-purple-700 bg-clip-text text-transparent font-semibold">R$ 0,00</span>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <!-- Compromisso com Transparência -->
  <Section
    title="Nosso Compromisso"
    className="bg-gray-50"
  >
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg border-2 border-blue-200 shadow-md">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 via-blue-700 to-blue-800 bg-clip-text text-transparent mb-4 drop-shadow-sm text-gradient-glow">
              Transparência Total
            </h3>
            <p class="bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-700 to-gray-800 bg-clip-text text-transparent mb-4 font-medium leading-relaxed">
              A A.R.L.S Enoch tem como um de seus valores fundamentais a transparência. Acreditamos que todos os doadores 
              têm o direito de saber como seus recursos estão sendo utilizados.
            </p>
            <p class="bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-700 to-gray-800 bg-clip-text text-transparent mb-4 font-medium">
              Por isso, mantemos esta página atualizada regularmente com:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mb-4">
              <li class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-blue-700 bg-clip-text text-transparent font-medium">
                Extratos mensais detalhados de receitas e despesas
              </li>
              <li class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-blue-700 bg-clip-text text-transparent font-medium">
                Informações sobre a destinação de cada recurso recebido
              </li>
              <li class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-blue-700 bg-clip-text text-transparent font-medium">
                Relatórios de impacto dos projetos financiados
              </li>
              <li class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-blue-700 bg-clip-text text-transparent font-medium">
                Demonstrações financeiras anuais
              </li>
            </ul>
            <p class="bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-700 to-gray-800 bg-clip-text text-transparent font-medium">
              Se tiver alguma dúvida sobre nossos relatórios ou quiser mais informações, não hesite em entrar em contato conosco.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>
</Layout>
